title: BBC - In Concert - Neil Young - 1971
description:
BBC - In Concert - Neil Young - 1971
Footage of the singer-songwriter from 1971, featuring songs that were eventually to feature on Young's classic album Harvest, including Heart of Gold, A Man Needs a Maid and Old Man.

Setlist
1. Out On The Weekend
2. Old Man
3. Journey Through The Past
4. Heart of Gold
5. Don't Let It Bring You Down
6. A Man Needs A Maid
7. Love In Mind
8. Dance Dance Dance

Recorded 23rd February 1971
BBC Television Theatre,
Shepherd's Bush, London.
